Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.index.schema

Class BlockEntry<KEY,​VALUE>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.index.schema.BlockEntry<KEY,​VALUE>
  • class BlockEntry<KEY,​VALUE>
extends Object
    A BlockEntry is a key-value mapping and the smallest unit in the BlockStorage and IndexUpdateStorage hierarchy. Except for being a container class for key-value pairs, it also provide static methods for serializing and deserializing BlockEntry instances and calculating total store size of them.
